OL,7,FThe regulator decided that bonuses
OL,8,Fshould be paid by shareholders instead
OL,9,Fof customers unless they have been
OL,10,F"earned", as ITV News' Martha Fairlie
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FNine water companies will be blocked
OL,14,Ffrom using customer money to fund
OL,15,F"undeserved" bonuses for top bosses
OL,16,Fworth #6.8 million, the water
OL,17,Fregulator has announced.
