OL,3,CNine water firms blocked from using
OL,4,Ccustomer cash to pay for #6.8m of
OL,5,Cbonuses
OL,7,FThis includes debt-laden Thames Water,
OL,8,Fwhich currently faces a funding crisis
OL,9,Fand owes more than #16 billion - and
OL,10,Fplanned to use customer cash to pay
OL,11,F#770,000 in bonuses for its chief
OL,12,Fexecutive Chris Weston and chief
OL,13,Ffinancial officer Alastair Cochran.
OL,15,FThe regulator Ofwat said it will use
OL,16,Fits new powers to stop companies from
OL,17,Fdigging into customer money to pay
OL,18,Fbonuses which can't be sufficiently
OL,19,Flinked to performance - amounting to
OL,20,F73% of total proposed awards across
OL,21,Fthe industry.
