OL,7,FYorkshire Water and Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,8,FWater are among the other firms
OL,9,Faffected, and along with Thames Water
OL,10,Fhave been directly blocked from
OL,11,Fallowing customers to pay #1.5 million
OL,12,Fof bonuses.
OL,14,FOfwat said a further six companies had
OL,15,Fvoluntarily decided not to push the
OL,16,Fcost of executive bonuses worth a
OL,17,Fcombined #5.2 million onto customers,
OL,18,Fwith shareholders paying instead.
