OL,3,CNine water firms blocked from using
OL,4,Ccustomer cash to pay for #6.8m of
OL,5,Cbonuses
OL,7,FDavid Black, chief executive of Ofwat,
OL,8,Fsaid: "In stopping customers from
OL,9,Fpaying for undeserved bonuses that do
OL,10,Fnot properly reflect performance, we
OL,11,Fare looking to sharpen executive
OL,12,Fmindsets and push companies to improve
OL,13,Ftheir performance and culture of
OL,14,Faccountability.
OL,16,F"While we are starting to see
OL,17,Fcompanies take some positive steps,
OL,18,Fthey need to do more to rebuild public
OL,19,Ftrust."
