OL,7,FSecretary of State for Environment,
OL,8,FFood and Rural Affairs Steve Reed
OL,9,Fsaid: "It is disgraceful that half of
OL,10,Fwater companies have given out
OL,11,Funjustifiable and unmerited bonuses.
OL,13,F"That is why this Government is
OL,14,Fintroducing urgent legislation to ban
OL,15,Fthe payment of unfair bonuses to
OL,16,Fpolluting water bosses so payouts of
OL,17,Fthis kind can never happen again."
